[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00661",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（人は誰しも仮面を被っているもの。\n　私はそう思ってる）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00662",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だって、完璧な人間なんていないじゃない？\n　だから一生懸命磨き上げた完璧な仮面で着飾るのよ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00663",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（幼い頃から、私は家族や周囲に「かわいい」とか、\n　「天才」とかしきりにほめられて育った）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00664",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だから私は自分のことをかわいくて天才で、\n　完璧なんだと思った。当たり前よね）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00665",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あの頃の私は今より素直だった。でも……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00666",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（大きくなるにつれて、私は知っていった。\n　いかに自分が完璧じゃないかを）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00667",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（意識した途端、素直になれなくなった。\n　本当の自分を見せるのが怖くなった）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00668",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そんな時、アイドルに出会った。\n　テレビ越しに見た、みんなの理想の体現）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00669",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（みんなはアイドルに理想を求め、\n　アイドルはみんなに理想を見せる）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00670",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（全員が一丸となってひたすらに理想を追い求める、\n　究極のステージ……いいなって、思った）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00671",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だって、そこには私はいなくてよくて。\n　みんなが期待する“ヨハナ”がいればいいから）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00672",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だから私は、私がみんなに見せたい理想の仮面を\n　被って、アイドルになる道を選んだ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00673",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（なのに）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00674",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……せっかく隠したんだから、\n仮面のほうを見てくれればいいのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00675",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……ええ、ぜひそちらの番組で取り上げて\nいただけないかと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00676",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……？　社長？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00677",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ディオーナと一緒であれば……？\n申し訳ありませんが、単独でお願いしたいですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00678",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "彼女たちをディオーナの添え物のようには\nしたくありません。ご期待に添えると信じています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00679",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ですから、ご再考いただけませんか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00680",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "本日アップされた動画はご覧になりまして？\n……ありがとうございます。それであれば話題性は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00681",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……分かりましたわ。いえ、ありがとうございます。\n今後ともごひいきに。では……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00682",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふう……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00683",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "必要以上の支援はしないって、言ってたくせに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00684",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら。なんのことですの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00685",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……あんたって、かっこいいわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00686",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "急にどうしまして？　あなたらしくもない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00687",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00688",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……格好付けているだけですわ。\n社長が堂々としていないと、下の者は不安でしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00689",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ついさっきまで、あんたがそんな仮面をつけてるなんて\n思ってもみなかったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00690",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "仮面……面白いたとえですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00691",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "私も、そんな仮面が欲しい。\n誰にもその下の姿が見えないような、そんな仮面",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00692",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "アイドルとして、みんなにいい面だけ見せてたい。\n素の私なんて見せたくないもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00693",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……そうですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00694",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ありのままの姿でいられたら楽でしょう。\nですが、あなたはそれを良しとしない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00695",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そう思って努力し、作り上げたあなたの姿……仮面。\nとても美しいと思いますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00696",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "わたくしは努力する者が好きです。\nあなたが仮面を被ることも、否定はいたしません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00697",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ですが、素のあなたの姿も、わたくしは好きですわよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00698",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "は、はあっ！？　嘘はやめなさいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00699",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "嘘ではありませんわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00700",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "絶対嘘。だってあんた、この前も「言い訳を並べるのは\n結構」ってイライラしてたじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00701",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あれはあなたを鼓舞するための言葉にすぎませんわ。\nそれに、１つあなたは気付いていないことがあります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00702",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたのことが好きでなければスカウトなどしません。\nわたくしが間違いなく、あなたのファン１号なのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00703",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00704",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "素のあなたも、仮面のあなたも。\nどちらも魅力的ですわ。自分に自信を持ちなさい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00705",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "う、うるさい！　ばーか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00706",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ばーか！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00707",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……かわいい。推しの新たな魅力ですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00708",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ、これだから社長はやめられませんわ。\n直接お金を投資する、究極の推し活なのですから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00709",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]